<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 01:29:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>模糊的基因组边界成为阿尔茨海默病生物学的新层面</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/blurred-genome-boundaries-emerge-as-a-new-layer-of-alzheimers-biology</link><description>卡内基梅隆大学计算机学院的研究人员&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/blurred-genome-boundaries-emerge-as-a-new-layer-of-alzheimers-biology2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 01:28:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/blurred-genome-boundaries-emerge-as-a-new-layer-of-alzheimers-biology</guid></item><item><title>完美的农药？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-perfect-pesticide</link><description>这种甲虫原产于落基山脉，现在遍布北半球，每年造成超过 5 亿美元的农作物损失。它是一个抵抗高手，让人难以控制。这种害虫是 20 世纪 30 年代开始化学农药研究的早期推动者。从那时起，它就进化出了对一种又一种化合物的免疫力——现在有 50 多种农药，代表了所有主要类型的活性成分。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-perfect-pesticide2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 01:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-perfect-pesticide</guid></item><item><title>动脉芯片有助于预测中风风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/artery-on-a-chip-helps-predict-stroke-risk</link><description>预测个人患缺血性中风的风险很困难，因为血栓栓塞（血凝块从其形成区域分离、移动然后粘在另一根血管中的过程）基于每个人独特的因素。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/artery-on-a-chip-helps-predict-stroke-risk.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 00:58:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/artery-on-a-chip-helps-predict-stroke-risk</guid></item><item><title>使用广义加性模型进行位置、尺度和形状的分布回归</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/distributional-regression-using-generalized-additive-models-for-location-scale-and-shape</link><description>分布回归对整个条件响应分布进行建模。在本入门书中，Merder &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/distributional-regression-using-generalized-additive-models-for-location-scale-and-shape.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 00:43:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/distributional-regression-using-generalized-additive-models-for-location-scale-and-shape</guid></item><item><title>认知细胞：思维是如何在大脑出现之前开始的</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-knowing-cell-how-mind-began-before-brains</link><description>从细胞骨架学习到意识信息架构&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-knowing-cell-how-mind-began-before-brains.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 00:28:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-knowing-cell-how-mind-began-before-brains</guid></item><item><title>Galaxy 推出比特币量子计算计划，承诺向开发者提供高达 500 万美元的资助</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/galaxy-launches-bitcoin-quantum-computing-initiative-commits-up-to-5-million-in-developer-grants</link><description>Galaxy 启动了比特币量子准备计划，包括承诺向开发者提供高达 500 万美元的资助。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/galaxy-launches-bitcoin-quantum-computing-initiative-commits-up-to-5-million-in-developer-grants.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 00:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/galaxy-launches-bitcoin-quantum-computing-initiative-commits-up-to-5-million-in-developer-grants</guid></item><item><title>Beehive 将 3D 打印无人机喷气发动机投入全面生产</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/beehive-pushes-3d-printed-drone-jet-engines-into-full-production</link><description>Beehive Industries 借助空军资金、30 台新打印机、机械车间以及 7000 万美元的俄亥俄州扩建项目，将 3D 打印喷气发动机的产量扩大到每年 8,000 台。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/beehive-pushes-3d-printed-drone-jet-engines-into-full-production.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 23:58:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/beehive-pushes-3d-printed-drone-jet-engines-into-full-production</guid></item><item><title>西北大学研究人员展示了繁忙电信光纤上的量子纠缠</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/northwestern-university-researchers-demonstrate-quantum-entanglement-over-busy-telecom-fiber</link><description>Kumar 和他的团队测得纠缠保真度超过 94%，证实它在整个旅程中幸存下来，达到了经典通信系统无法重现的水平。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/northwestern-university-researchers-demonstrate-quantum-entanglement-over-busy-telecom-fiber.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 23:43:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/northwestern-university-researchers-demonstrate-quantum-entanglement-over-busy-telecom-fiber</guid></item><item><title>2017 年诺贝尔物理学奖</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/nobel-prize-in-physics-2017</link><description>2017 年诺贝尔物理学奖被平分，一半颁发给 Rainer Weiss，另一半共同颁发给 Barry C. Barish 和 Kip S. Thorne，以表彰“对 LIGO 探测器和引力波观测的决定性贡献”&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nobel-prize-in-physics-2017.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 23:28:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/nobel-prize-in-physics-2017</guid></item><item><title>镰状细胞病中的血液干细胞过早衰老可能是可逆的</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/premature-blood-stem-cell-aging-in-sickle-cell-disease-may-be-reversible</link><description>圣裘德儿童研究医院的一项新研究表明，镰状细胞病会导致造血干细胞过早衰老，科学家们或许可以用一类特殊的药物来解决这一问题。与同龄人相比，镰状细胞病患者患造血干细胞功能障碍和血癌的几率更高，但原因尚不清楚。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/premature-blood-stem-cell-aging-in-sickle-cell-disease-may-be-reversible.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 23:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/premature-blood-stem-cell-aging-in-sickle-cell-disease-may-be-reversible</guid></item></channel></rss>